  title="Contact us - Boomger."
  description="About us - Boomger. - One Night Stand Entertainment, the innovative force behind One Night, the premier dating app designed to connect people for whatever they seekâ€”be it a spark, a relationship, a date, a hookup, or a one-night stand. We are committed to creating an inclusive and dynamic platform that caters to diverse romantic and social needs."
>
  <main
    class="mx-6 sm:mx-12 lg:mx-24 mb-20 max-w-7xl py-12 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-22.75 text-lg min-h-[calc(100vh-576px)] items-center md:w-[-webkit-fill-available]"
  >
    <div
      class="border rounded-[20px] pt-6.5 lg:pt-10 lg:pb-20 pb-17.5 px-4 w-full sm:px-8"
    >
      <p class="text-2xl sm:text-[32px] mb-7.5 lg:mb-9">
        Have an inquiry or <br /> complaint? contact US
